text:
(Toru's been gone for a while since she went to buy
souvenirs. She might be lost, I should go pick herup...)

Toru...!
It took you a while, I was worried.

Huh... oh, sorry.
I was looking for something I wanted.

Oh, you were looking for something?
...But you can buy that even in Tokyo.

Huh?
Oh... hehe, I didn't know.
